Dia. 02 Big Mistake
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Trying to go out with 1 is a \cf1\b big mistake\cf0\b0 .
\par After the exchange for Black 2, even if Lee Chang-ho 9p comes, he can't save this White group.
\par
\par If White plays the tiger's mouth move at 3, Black's \cf2\b placement\cf0\b0  at 4 is \cf2\b severe\cf0\b0 .
\par White dies up to 6.
\par
\par If White plays the tiger's mouth move at 4 instead of 3, Black plays the placement at 3 and White is dead again.
\par
\par }
