Dia. 03 Better than Nothing
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par How about expanding the eye-space with White 1? If Black plays at 2, White can resist with the tiger's mouth move at 3.
\par
\par After Black 4, White makes pae with 5. White couldn't live unconditionally but it is still better than nothing.
\par
\par However there was a \cf1\b mistake\cf0\b0  in \b this\b0  \b sequence\b0 . If Black plays the placement at 3 instead of 2, White can't live.
\par }
